<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>ArmorAuth 激活完成</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/armorauth-ui.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-shell">
    <main class="center-card">
        <div class="section-title">
            <span class="eyebrow">Completed</span>
            <h1>设备已完成激活</h1>
            <p>授权已经写回设备会话。现在可以回到你的设备继续下一步操作。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="notice success">
            如果设备侧没有自动刷新，请手动返回上一页重新进入。
        </div>
        <div class="action-row">
            <a class="button primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
            <a class="button secondary" href="/login">返回登录页</a>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>
</body>
</html>
